720458f-a.title: Manhattan: Hubert Street - Greenwich Street
720458f-a.text:
Hubert Street, south side, east from Greenwich to Hudson Streets,
showing under demolition, Nos. 13-11, a 6-story warehouse at the S.W.
corner of Collister Street. Occupying the opposite corner is a 5-story
structure formerly P.S. 44.
August 2, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
